source.name: Cash for Clunkers Separated by Make
source.description: This following list is based on the requirements set forth in the Cash for Clunkers program (officially known as the Consumer Assistance to Recycle and Save Act, or CARS) that was enacted on June 24, 2009, as well as the published regulations issued by the National Highway Traffic Safety Administration ("NHTSA") on July 24, 2009.
